Hello all,

I just wanted to let you know that we have increased the resolu=
tion on EndlessForms.com, but it **only applies to newly evolved objects**.=
 That allows older artistic choices to remain unaffected by the higher reso=
lution, but allows the community to explore an increased and more exciting =
design space. 

Please try it out by clicking on any shape you like here: 
=

http://endlessforms.com/

For some of the objects that have a lot of surfa=
ce area, things get a lot slower, but we hope that it is worth it to push t=
he cutting edge of what is possible. 

Example that is cool, but slower, at=
 high res:
Low res: http://endlessforms.com/o/692722/
High res: http://endl=
essforms.com/g/s9sif4ws3c_0/


Happy holidays. 

Best regards,
Jeff Clune

=
Visiting Scientist
Cornell University
jeffclune@...
jeffclune.com
